Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Carter's civil defence policy
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bs67
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 25 Jun 1978
President Carter backtracks on civil defence. Debate over US policy on USSR. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.